There, child. Yes.

186
00:19:25,375 --> 00:19:27,291
- I'll close the door, okay?
- Okay.

187
00:19:40,833 --> 00:19:42,958
Everything's okay, child?

188
00:19:43,041 --> 00:19:44,416
Yes, Mom.

189
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:13,166
Gendis, are you done?

190
00:20:18,458 --> 00:20:19,666
Gendis?

191
00:20:23,625 --> 00:20:24,916
Gendis?

192
00:20:37,375 --> 00:20:38,625
Gendis?

193
00:20:41,041 --> 00:20:42,333
Gendis?

194
00:20:45,583 --> 00:20:46,666
Gendis?

195
00:20:48,291 --> 00:20:49,458
Are you done?

196
00:20:52,541 --> 00:20:53,750
I'm done.

197
00:20:54,583 --> 00:20:55,958
Let's go.

198
00:20:56,625 --> 00:20:58,000
