212
00:23:24,708 --> 00:23:27,000
SEMARANG, CENTRAL JAVA

213
00:23:27,083 --> 00:23:32,625
Your duties are only administration
and registration.

214
00:23:38,208 --> 00:23:42,041
Sometimes accident victims like this...

215
00:23:42,125 --> 00:23:43,583
...have no identification.

216
00:23:43,666 --> 00:23:45,833
So, you try to find it.

217
00:23:45,916 --> 00:23:48,708
You trace the family.

218
00:23:50,250 --> 00:23:52,250
If they don't have any, then...

219
00:23:52,333 --> 00:23:53,583
...we'll take care of them.

220
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:03,291
Sir...

221
00:24:03,375 --> 00:24:07,000
...regarding the subsidy program
for employees with children...

222
00:24:07,083 --> 00:24:10,125
...I'm planning to get eye surgery
for my child.

223
00:24:11,375 --> 00:24:14,083
She has a congenital condition,
something like cataracts.

224
00:24:15,708 --> 00:24:17,250
Yes, we have one.

225
00:24:17,333 --> 00:24:21,666
After you've worked for a year...

226
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:24,916
...there's a 50 percent subsidy
from the hospital...

227
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:29,000
...for all types of procedures.
Including eye surgery.

228
00:24:29,916 --> 00:24:33,958
Just ask the administration for details.

229
00:24:34,416 --> 00:24:36,541
- Anything else you want to ask?
- That's it, sir.

230
00:24:37,583 --> 00:24:38,583
Anto.

231
00:24:40,250 --> 00:24:42,000
Just in time.

232
00:24:43,291 --> 00:24:45,208
This is Mr. Anto.

233
00:24:45,291 --> 00:24:47,958
Our ambulance administrator...

234
