...if anyone calls you...

550
00:52:56,000 --> 00:52:58,708
...if anyone invites you...

551
00:52:58,791 --> 00:53:01,375
...if your neck gets stiff...

552
00:53:01,458 --> 00:53:03,416
...just refuse.

553
00:53:04,125 --> 00:53:07,125
Don't let them in.

554
00:53:08,125 --> 00:53:09,125
Okay?

555
00:53:32,208 --> 00:53:34,208
The important thing is...

556
00:53:34,875 --> 00:53:36,708
...get her to drink this later.

557
00:53:37,666 --> 00:53:40,250
And here's another bottle...

558
00:53:40,333 --> 00:53:42,166
Pour it around the house.

559
00:53:42,583 --> 00:53:45,500
And don't forget the young coconut.

560
00:53:49,750 --> 00:53:52,041
I've been worried
about this from the start.

561
00:53:52,583 --> 00:53:53,750
Yes, but you didn't...

562
00:53:55,041 --> 00:53:56,500
Drink this first.

563
00:54:04,000 --> 00:54:06,166
The stall you saw
over there doesn't exist.

564
00:54:07,125 --> 00:54:08,791
There's no lady, no one.

565
00:54:08,875 --> 00:54:11,333
- Anto.
- There's only wilderness...

566
00:54:11,416 --> 00:54:13,166
...and creatures we can't see.

567
00:54:13,250 --> 00:54:16,500
The bus broke down, the magical food stall
that you and Gendis saw...

568
00:54:16,583 --> 00:54:17,541
...was already a sign.

569
00:54:18,625 --> 00:54:20,000
What sign?

570
00:54:20,791 --> 00:54:21,916
here's something supernatural...

571
00:54:22,416 --> 00:54:23,750
...following you...

572
00:54:24,958 --> 00:54:26,000
...or Gendis.

573
00:54:29,416 --> 00:54:32,125
Anto, please speak more slowly.

574
00:54:32,208 --> 00:54:33,750
Sita doesn't understand things like this.

575
00:54:33,833 --> 00:54:36,166
You know what happened
to my wife and child.

576
00:54:36,250 --> 00:54:37,500
Yes, I understand.

577
00:54:37,583 --> 00:54:39,750
- But I can't...
- What's going on?

578
00:55:06,583 --> 00:55:09,000
Do you want to come with me?

579
00:55:12,500 --> 00:55:15,583
My wife and child disappeared
while passing through Alas Roban at night.

580
00:55:15,666 --> 00:55:18,333
Just like you,
they took a night bus trip...

581
00:55:18,416 --> 00:55:20,500
...even though I had forbidden them.

582
00:55:20,583 --> 00:55:21,833
They were found.

583
00:55:22,458 --> 00:55:24,958
Their bodies were found a month later.

584
00:55:25,041 --> 00:55:26,500
On the side of the road.

585
00:55:27,958 --> 00:55:29,291
Oh, God!

586
00:55:31,416 --> 00:55:33,125
Honey...

587
00:55:33,208 --> 00:55:36,416
The Alas Roban myth really happened
to my wife and child.

588
00:55:36,500 --> 00:55:39,083
I'm saying this
because I don't want any more victims.

589
00:55:39,166 --> 00:55:42,041
You can't just use some
kind of bottled water or coconut water.

590
00:55:42,125 --> 00:55:43,208
No way.

591
00:55:43,291 --> 00:55:44,958
We have to get help.

592
00:55:45,041 --> 00:55:46,833
Where should we go?

593
00:55:46,916 --> 00:55:48,375
I have an acquaintance.

594
00:55:48,458 --> 00:55:49,583
His name is Mbah Rejo.

595
00:55:49,916 --> 00:55:51,541
He usually handles things like this.

596
00:56:43,208 --> 00:56:44,083
Mom...

597
00:56:47,375 --> 00:56:48,625
Mom!

598
00:56:50,625 --> 00:56:51,625
Gendis?

599
00:56:54,208 --> 00:56:55,041
Gendis!

600
00:56:57,666 --> 00:56:58,666
Gendis!

601
00:56:59,541 --> 00:57:00,916
Gendis, wake up.

602
00:57:02,750 --> 00:57:04,333
Child, it's me, your mom!

603
00:57:04,416 --> 00:57:05,916
Gendis.

604
00:57:06,000 --> 00:57:07,333
Mom!

605
00:57:08,333 --> 00:57:10,625
Gendis. It's me.

606
00:57:10,708 --> 00:57:11,791
Tika.

607
00:57:11,875 --> 00:57:14,208
- Gendis!
- Mom!

608
00:57:16,208 --> 00:57:17,791
- Gendis.
- It's no use.

609
00:57:17,875 --> 00:57:19,041
It won't work.

610
00:57:20,250 --> 00:57:21,916
We have to take her to Mbah Rejo's place.

611
00:57:23,458 --> 00:57:24,958
Sita.

612
00:57:25,500 --> 00:57:27,041
We have to get out of here, Sita.

613
00:57:29,250 --> 00:57:30,375
We have to take Gendis.

614
00:57:31,166 --> 00:57:32,583
Come on.

615
00:57:33,750 --> 00:57:34,875
Gendis...

616
00:57:38,625 --> 00:57:39,583
Gendis...

617
00:57:47,833 --> 00:57:49,083
There's a power...

618
00:57:49,708 --> 00:57:50,875
...that's unusual...

619
00:57:52,416 --> 00:57:54,000
...in this child's body.

620
00:57:56,458 --> 00:57:57,916
An evil force...

621
00:58:00,583 --> 00:58:02,416
...wants to control her body.

622
00:58:23,916 --> 00:58:24,750
Gendis.

623
00:58:26,500 --> 00:58:28,541
Kid.

624
00:58:28,625 --> 00:58:30,250
Kid!

625
00:58:30,333 --> 00:58:31,375
Gendis.

626
00:58:31,458 --> 00:58:33,083
Mbah, what's wrong with her?

627
00:58:33,166 --> 00:58:34,291
Gendis.

628
00:58:52,416 --> 00:58:53,541
Gendis.

629
00:58:59,375 --> 00:59:01,666
You're on the wrong path.

630
00:59:02,791 --> 00:59:05,416
You humans...

631
00:59:05,500 --> 00:59:07,583
...don't understand.

632
00:59:11,666 --> 00:59:12,541
Gendis.

633
00:59:15,916 --> 00:59:18,416
I...

634
00:59:18,500 --> 00:59:20,708
...ask for God's protection.

635
00:59:23,416 --> 00:59:26,083
The remaining soul...

636
00:59:26,875 --> 00:59:30,000
...may the path back home
be made easy to eternity.

637
00:59:34,000 --> 00:59:35,041
Gendis!

638
00:59:36,750 --> 00:59:38,666
- It's me.
- Gendis.

639
00:59:38,958 --> 00:59:40,083
Gendis...

640
00:59:45,083 --> 00:59:46,875
Mbah, what's wrong with her?

641
00:59:47,333 --> 00:59:48,708
What's wrong with her?

642
01:00:10,250 --> 01:00:11,833
Tika!

643
01:00:16,625 --> 01:00:18,041
You're...

644
01:00:20,458 --> 01:00:23,041
...going the wrong way, Rejo.

645
01:00:32,625 --> 01:00:34,875
That kid...

646
01:00:36,750 --> 01:00:39,750
...would rather be with me.

647
01:00:42,625 --> 01:00:43,708
No!

648
01:00:46,125 --> 01:00:48,083
Poor thing.

649
01:00:52,916 --> 01:00:55,125
Still not letting them go?

650
01:00:57,291 --> 01:00:58,125
Mbah.

651
01:00:58,583 --> 01:01:00,291
Leave this woman's body!

652
01:01:00,375 --> 01:01:01,208
Go away!

653
01:01:07,416 --> 01:01:09,875
It's not her body...

654
01:01:10,791 --> 01:01:13,208
...that you should be worried about.

655
01:01:17,666 --> 01:01:19,791
It's her soul.

656
01:01:19,875 --> 01:01:22,166
Go back to where you came from!
Go home!

657
01:01:30,375 --> 01:01:34,625
I ask for God's protection.

658
01:01:36,708 --> 01:01:40,375
The soul of Dewi Raras...

659
01:01:42,833 --> 01:01:45,250
- Tika...
- ...that still remains...

660
01:01:45,333 --> 01:01:47,791
...may the path home be made easy...

661
01:01:48,791 --> 01:01:50,958
...towards eternity.

662
01:01:55,708 --> 01:01:57,375
Tika...

663
01:01:58,500 --> 01:01:59,666
Tika!

664
01:02:03,125 --> 01:02:04,750
Tika.

665
01:02:21,083 --> 01:02:21,958
Tika!

666
01:02:23,416 --> 01:02:24,583
Tika?

667
01:02:25,041 --> 01:02:27,000
Tika!

668
01:02:32,208 --> 01:02:33,041
Gendis.

669
01:02:34,583 --> 01:02:36,166
- Gendis?
- Tika...

670
01:02:41,833 --> 01:02:43,625
Tika, are you okay?

671
01:02:44,041 --> 01:02:45,041
Tika...

672
01:02:47,791 --> 01:02:49,458
Dewi Raras' soul...

673
01:02:51,500 --> 01:02:54,500
...the one who inhabits Alas Roban...

674
01:02:56,833 --> 01:02:58,083
It's too strong.

675
01:02:58,791 --> 01:03:00,750
Is that the figure following Gendis?

676
01:03:04,041 --> 01:03:04,875
Yes.

677
01:03:05,833 --> 01:03:11,541
But I'm sorry, I can't help you.

678
01:03:14,083 --> 01:03:15,125
Gendis.

679
01:03:17,791 --> 01:03:20,000
I'm sorry, okay?

680
01:03:23,791 --> 01:03:28,041
I haven't been able
to give you a perfect life.

681
01:03:37,500 --> 01:03:39,291
I'm sorry.

682
01:04:07,541 --> 01:04:09,583
The bus he was driving pass midnight...

683
01:04:09,666 --> 01:04:11,375
...plunged into a ravine...

684
01:04:11,625 --> 01:04:12,791
...on a sharp bend...

685
01:04:12,875 --> 01:04:14,250
...and a steep incline...

686
01:04:14,541 --> 01:04:15,500
...in Alas Roban.

687
01:04:16,375 --> 01:04:18,333
People usually call it...

688
01:04:19,166 --> 01:04:20,375
...Skull Path.

689
01:04:22,375 --> 01:04:24,125
Ma'am.
Excuse me.

690
01:04:25,916 --> 01:04:28,791
We just found the bus driver's body
at the scene...

691
01:04:28,958 --> 01:04:30,125
...while the bodies
of the other passengers

692
01:04:30,208 --> 01:04:31,166
have not yet been found.

693
01:04:43,291 --> 01:04:47,083
The bus driver who took me...

694
01:04:47,791 --> 01:04:50,958
...passed Alas Roban that night...

695
01:04:51,750 --> 01:04:53,041
...died.

696
01:04:56,041 --> 01:04:59,500
His body was taken to the hospital.

697
01:05:08,958 --> 01:05:10,125
Gendis.

698
01:05:16,958 --> 01:05:18,250
Gendis.

699
01:05:25,375 --> 01:05:26,458
Mom.

700
01:05:37,541 --> 01:05:38,458
Gendis?

701
01:05:42,416 --> 01:05:43,416
Gendis?

702
01:07:06,708 --> 01:07:07,541
Gendis?

703
01:07:13,000 --> 01:07:13,916
Gendis?

704
01:07:20,625 --> 01:07:21,458
Gendis.

705
01:07:26,208 --> 01:07:27,208
Gendis.

706
01:07:31,916 --> 01:07:34,541
You don't love me.

707
01:07:36,416 --> 01:07:38,375
Because I'm blind.

708
01:07:39,166 --> 01:07:41,166
Because I'm blind.

709
01:07:41,666 --> 01:07:43,875
Because I'm blind!

710
01:07:49,875 --> 01:07:51,458
My child!

711
01:07:51,541 --> 01:07:52,541
My child!

712
01:08:49,708 --> 01:08:52,541
Sita, this is a white monkey.

713
01:08:53,041 --> 01:08:54,833
Are you sure Gendis drew this?

714
01:08:55,250 --> 01:08:56,541
Who else?

715
01:08:57,666 --> 01:08:59,375
Isn't white monkey...

716
01:09:00,833 --> 01:09:02,500
...a myth that exists in Alas Roban?

717
01:09:07,083 --> 01:09:09,583
The woman who was at the hospital...

718
01:09:09,666 --> 01:09:10,583
Mrs. Ema?

719
01:09:10,666 --> 01:09:12,500
That woman said something
about a white monkey.

720
01:09:12,583 --> 01:09:15,125
She even knew I had seen a white monkey.

721
01:09:15,500 --> 01:09:16,791
You also said that...

722
01:09:16,875 --> 01:09:18,958
...that she knows a lot about Alas Roban?

723
01:09:19,541 --> 01:09:20,833
She is quite famous.

724
01:09:20,916 --> 01:09:23,541
The locals call her Pengayom Pasarean.

725
01:09:24,125 --> 01:09:25,416
A sacred caretaker.

726
01:09:25,500 --> 01:09:27,458
But as far as I know,
she's not like Mbah Rejo,

727
01:09:27,541 --> 01:09:28,750
who usually handles things like this.

728
01:09:28,833 --> 01:09:30,541
Well, I have to at least try.

729
01:09:32,583 --> 01:09:34,041
I have to meet her.

730
01:09:34,333 --> 01:09:35,958
There's no time left.

731
01:09:36,500 --> 01:09:39,000
Anto, do you know
where Mrs. Ema's house is?

732
01:10:23,750 --> 01:10:25,166
You're too late.

733
01:10:26,333 --> 01:10:28,458
This child is already in Alur Gembok.

734
01:10:30,625 --> 01:10:32,750
This is the gate.

735
01:10:33,958 --> 01:10:37,416
Where you saw the white monkey.

736
01:10:38,875 --> 01:10:43,541
Anyone who sees it
will experience misfortune.

737
01:10:49,416 --> 01:10:52,750
Alas Roban used to be just a wilderness.

738
01:10:53,250 --> 01:10:54,833
It supported life.

739
01:10:56,041 --> 01:10:58,375
Until Ki Bahurekso arrived.

740
01:10:59,000 --> 01:11:02,916
By envoy
of Sultan Hanyokrokusumo of Mataram.

741
01:11:06,291 --> 01:11:08,458
He divided the wilderness...

742
01:11:08,791 --> 01:11:10,958
...for human civilization.

743
01:11:13,750 --> 01:11:17,583
Asphalt was laid
from upstream to downstream.

744
01:11:18,000 --> 01:11:22,750
He is known for his success
in conquering the Alas Roban demons.

745
01:11:23,708 --> 01:11:27,708
But what was agreed upon at that time
has been violated.

746
01:11:27,958 --> 01:11:32,791
People instead turned Alas Roban
into a place of filth.

747
01:11:34,583 --> 01:11:38,041
This forest was used as a dumping ground

748
01:11:38,125 --> 01:11:40,333
for the bodies of victims
during the colonial era.

749
01:11:43,500 --> 01:11:48,083
And this is what sparked the anger
of the guardians of Alas Roban.

750
01:11:59,208 --> 01:12:00,416
Dewi Raras...

751
01:12:02,125 --> 01:12:04,791
...she is known as the guardian of Alas
Roban.

752
01:12:07,541 --> 01:12:09,541
It was Dewi Raras' anger...

753
01:12:10,375 --> 01:12:16,541
...that made her try to invite anyone
who passed through Alas Roban at night...

754
01:12:16,916 --> 01:12:19,041
...to join her world.

755
01:12:20,666 --> 01:12:24,708
To this day, many terrifying stories
have emerged in Alas Roban.

756
01:12:25,875 --> 01:12:28,833
And that's what happened to your daughter.

757
01:12:35,583 --> 01:12:37,500
Isn't there anything we can do, Ma'am?

758
01:12:38,791 --> 01:12:41,041
It's too late now.

759
01:12:41,833 --> 01:12:44,375
Because anyone trapped in the Alur
Gembok...

760
01:12:46,250 --> 01:12:49,416
...has less than seven days...

761
01:12:49,750 --> 01:12:51,708
...to make it out alive.

762
01:12:53,083 --> 01:12:54,083
Unless...

763
01:12:55,250 --> 01:12:57,458
...we all return to Alas Roban...

764
01:12:57,666 --> 01:12:58,750
...bringing your child.

765
01:13:04,166 --> 01:13:05,166
Sita, wait.

766
01:13:06,083 --> 01:13:07,125
Sita!

767
01:13:07,833 --> 01:13:09,458
Sita, wait.

768
01:13:09,666 --> 01:13:11,250
We have to try.

769
01:13:11,916 --> 01:13:12,750
Maybe...

770
01:13:13,166 --> 01:13:15,541
...this is the best way to save Gendis.

771
01:13:15,625 --> 01:13:16,875
You heard it yourself, right?

772
01:13:16,958 --> 01:13:19,083
Gendis was asked by the guardian there.

773
01:13:19,541 --> 01:13:20,708
And what's the way out?

774
01:13:21,375 --> 01:13:22,875
Bring Gendis back there?

775
01:13:24,250 --> 01:13:28,166
Who can guarantee that she isn't in league
with the guardian of Alas Roban?

776
01:13:29,583 --> 01:13:31,083
I don't want to go back there.

777
01:13:31,708 --> 01:13:34,333
This is a suicide mission for all of us.

778
01:13:34,791 --> 01:13:36,291
If I were you...

779
01:13:36,791 --> 01:13:39,541
...I would kill myself for my child.

780
01:13:41,583 --> 01:13:43,000
And if Gendis survives...

781
01:13:44,833 --> 01:13:47,208
...who will she live with
if we're not here?

782
01:14:21,166 --> 01:14:22,041
Gendis?

783
01:14:25,666 --> 01:14:26,500
Gendis?

784
01:14:33,500 --> 01:14:34,333
Gendis!

785
01:14:37,083 --> 01:14:39,416
My child!

786
01:14:39,500 --> 01:14:41,125
Gendis!

787
01:14:42,208 --> 01:14:43,250
Gendis!

788
01:14:45,000 --> 01:14:45,916
Gendis!

789
01:14:46,000 --> 01:14:47,833
Sir, help me!

790
01:14:48,208 --> 01:14:49,375
Yes, ma'am.

791
01:15:17,041 --> 01:15:17,875
Sita.

792
01:15:18,375 --> 01:15:20,625
Mrs. Ema told me
that something's wrong with Gendis.

793
01:15:21,250 --> 01:15:22,958
How is she? Is she getting better?

794
01:15:30,500 --> 01:15:32,000
She's getting farther away.

795
01:15:35,291 --> 01:15:37,208
Time is running out.

796
01:15:41,375 --> 01:15:43,416
If you don't want to lose her...

797
01:15:44,166 --> 01:15:46,166
...we have to go back there immediately.

798
01:15:46,750 --> 01:15:48,458
Before the day changes.

799
01:15:48,916 --> 01:15:50,166
The longer it takes...

800
01:15:51,250 --> 01:15:53,250
...the harder it is to save her.

801
01:16:04,375 --> 01:16:05,208
Gendis.

802
01:16:06,666 --> 01:16:07,958
Gendis, it's me, your mom.

803
01:16:08,041 --> 01:16:09,291
Gendis!

804
01:16:09,375 --> 01:16:11,250
Call the doctor!

805
01:16:16,250 --> 01:16:17,708
There's no other way.

806
01:16:18,125 --> 01:16:19,875
We have to go to Alas Roban now.

807
01:16:19,958 --> 01:16:21,666
What should I do?

808
01:17:13,416 --> 01:17:14,416
Can you?

809
01:17:31,416 --> 01:17:33,250
Everything has been prepared.

810
01:17:38,666 --> 01:17:40,666
They already know we're coming.

811
01:18:00,041 --> 01:18:01,041
Lay her down.

812
01:19:11,958 --> 01:19:15,875
O Most Gracious and Most Merciful God.

813
01:19:18,541 --> 01:19:21,625
Forgive all mistakes of men...

814
01:19:23,000 --> 01:19:25,583
...who are involved in many sins.

815
01:19:30,291 --> 01:19:34,000
I'm begging before the ancestors...

816
01:19:34,791 --> 01:19:38,083
...to open the invisible gate.

817
01:19:38,166 --> 01:19:41,000
I come with a pure heart.

818
01:19:41,916 --> 01:19:44,958
Don't disturb bad things.

819
01:19:46,375 --> 01:19:48,875
I hope I'll be granted entry...

820
01:19:50,458 --> 01:19:54,125
...and return home safely.

821
01:20:03,791 --> 01:20:06,250
They won't let me in.

822
01:20:09,291 --> 01:20:11,750
There's nothing else we can do.

823
01:20:25,833 --> 01:20:27,291
Can I try?

824
01:20:27,583 --> 01:20:29,333
Sita.

825
01:20:40,958 --> 01:20:43,000
Sita, don't.

826
