01:49:09,916 --> 01:49:12,000
...there is a wayang performance, sir.

1111
01:49:12,083 --> 01:49:15,875
If there is no wayang performance,
sometimes there are disasters.

1112
01:49:15,958 --> 01:49:16,791
Disaster.

1113
01:49:16,875 --> 01:49:19,000
The supernatural spirit is here.

1114
01:49:19,083 --> 01:49:20,875
In the Poncowati area.

1115
01:49:20,958 --> 01:49:25,208
Around Poncowati, it's called
Gunung Tunggal. White tiger.

1116
01:49:25,291 --> 01:49:29,000
- The forest here has been cleared.
- But there are a lot of tigers.

1117
01:49:29,083 --> 01:49:33,208
But they're not real tigers,
they're ghosts.

1118
01:49:33,291 --> 01:49:35,500
Some saw them, some didn't.

1119
01:50:15,916 --> 01:50:16,916
ALAS ROBAN HAS LONG BEEN KNOWN
FOR VARIOUS THINGS,

1120
01:50:17,000 --> 01:50:18,000
FOLKLORE THAT IS EMBEDDED
IN PEOPLE'S MINDS

1121
01:50:18,083 --> 01:50:19,041
NOW, THE AREA AROUND ALAS ROBAN
HAS UNDERGONE MANY CHANGES.

1122
01:50:19,125 --> 01:50:20,375
VARIOUS INFRASTRUCTURE DEVELOPMENTS
CONTINUE TO BE BUILT.

1123
01:50:20,458 --> 01:50:21,458
THIS AREA HAS EVEN TRANSFORMED INTO
AN INTEGRATED INDUSTRIAL AREA.

1124
01:50:21,541 --> 01:50:22,416
NEVERTHELESS, THE IDENTITY OF ALAS ROBAN

1125
01:50:22,500 --> 01:50:23,625
REMAINS THE RESULT
OF VERY LONG HISTORICAL ROOTS

1126
01:50:23,708 --> 01:50:24,708
...FROM THE STORIES AND NOBLE VALUES
THAT LIVE IN SOCIETY.

1127
01:50:24,875 --> 01:50:25,958
REGENT OF BATANG REGENCY

1128
01:50:30,083 --> 01:50:31,333
THIS STORY IS A WORK OF FICTION.

1129
01:50:31,416 --> 01:50:32,625
ANY SIMILARITIES IN NAMES, CHARACTERS,
PLACES, OR EVENTS...

1130
01:50:32,708 --> 01:50:33,958
...WITH REAL PEOPLE OR EVENTS ARE
SOLELY COINCIDENCE...

1131
01:50:34,041 --> 01:50:35,208
...AND NOT INTENDED INTENTIONALLY.

